{"tid":575504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一表睇晒】增6,700個公務員職位 新增職位最多是警務處","createTime":"2018-02-28T08:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:27:26.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd728cf808196b29bebf265c329cbcadd91fe57","tid":575504,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"【一表睇晒】增6,700個公務員職位 邊十個部門請最多人?<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波今早在立法會發表2018/19年度財政預算案，政府將會增加人手以配合推行各項新政策和措施，並減輕公務員工作壓力。在18/19年度公務員編制將增加至188,451個職位，較上年度增加6,700個，增幅約為3.7%，屬回歸以來按年增幅最高。此外亦會一筆過向政策局調撥資源，相等於各政策局經常開支封套非薪酬部份的3%。政府指，下年度增聘的6,700個公務員職位，7成屬前線人員，3,100個職位來自紀律部隊。<br />\n<br />\n【十大新增職位所屬政府部門】 <br />\n部門：新增職位數目<br />\n1. 警務處：1,057<br />\n2. 入境處：824<br />\n3. 香港海關：766<br />\n4. 消防處：383<br />\n5. 地政總署：378<br />\n6. 社會福利署：292<br />\n7. 房委會：251<br />\n8. 康文署：242<br />\n9. 環保署：211<br />\n10. 衛生署：183<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：預算編制摘要<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180228/57886366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180228%2F57886366&d=uCRaRgrXmGIwlsKB%2FNEPtV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3e3fcf07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180228%2F57886366&h=1694a3e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180228/57886366</a>"},{"pid":"0b804b567aef30194f97cc29581397ae7c54bd63","tid":575504,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"警察出名懶"},{"pid":"6b4c471d14168dd87de1656638276eba3294de32","tid":575504,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"政府指，下年度增聘的6,700個公務員職位，7成屬前線人員，<span style=\"color: red;\">3,100個職位來自紀律部隊</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc307ad6726dff3475f24e32ad542a4f5a2227d7","tid":575504,"uid":76747,"like":0,"